#: blog/source/blog/2015-07-07-coming-soon-new-home-page-and-wiki/index.adoc:140
#, no-wrap
msgid "Free and open source"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: blog/source/blog/2015-07-07-coming-soon-new-home-page-and-wiki/index.adoc:142
